OL,3,CProtest planned over 'iconic' Lido
OL,4,Cafter owner negotiations break down
OL,6,FA St Helier pressure group are
OL,7,Fplanning to stage a protest over what
OL,8,Fthey say are "excessive" delays to
OL,9,Fownership negotiations surrounding the
OL,10,FHavre des Pas Lido.
OL,12,FThe Lido Steering Group's chair,
OL,13,FDeputy David Warr, revealed that 'Love
OL,14,FOur Lido' - a community-run venture -
OL,15,Fhad lost its status as the "preferred
OL,16,Fbidder" to take over the public
OL,17,Foutdoor pool at the end of September.
