OL,3,CProtest planned over 'iconic' Lido
OL,4,Cafter owner negotiations break down
OL,6,FDeputy Warr says a protest will be
OL,7,Fheld in the Royal Square ahead of a
OL,8,FStates sitting on Tuesday 11 November
OL,9,F"if meaningful negotiations are not re-
OL,10,Fengaged by early November".
OL,12,FHe adds that the collapse of the 'Love
OL,13,FOur Lido' bid, led by local
OL,14,Fbusinessman Matt Falla, stemmed from
OL,15,F"several fundamental issues",
OL,16,Fincluding concerns over a lack of
OL,17,Ffunding for maintenance and
OL,18,Foutstanding utility invoices that
OL,19,Fcould become the responsibility of
OL,20,Fvolunteers.
