OL,3,CProtest planned over 'iconic' Lido
OL,4,Cafter owner negotiations break down
OL,6,FHe explains: "The #60,000 annual
OL,7,F'backstop' offered by JPH is wholly
OL,8,Finsufficient, as the true annual cost
OL,9,Fof maintaining the site, according to
OL,10,Fpublic record, is around #120,000.
OL,12,F"Furthermore, every 10 years, a
OL,13,Ffurther #500,000 is typically required
OL,14,Ffor major decoration and structural
OL,15,Fupkeep, taking the annual cost to
OL,16,Fapproximately #170,000.
OL,18,F"The Lido is an iconic site, and I
OL,19,Fdon't think the people of Jersey would
OL,20,Ftolerate it being lost."
