OL,3,CProtest planned over 'iconic' Lido
OL,4,Cafter owner negotiations break down
OL,6,FThe Lido Steering Group's frustrations
OL,7,Fover the pool's ownership have been
OL,8,Fcompounded by what they describe as "a
OL,9,Ftroubling lack of transparency" over
OL,10,Fthe site's electricity and water bills.
OL,12,FDeputy Warr claims: "Significant
OL,13,Ffluctuations have been reported, and
OL,14,Frequests to see original supplier
OL,15,Finvoices have not been met."
OL,17,FThe Constable for St Helier, Simon
OL,18,FCrowcroft, believes Deputy Warr is
OL,19,Fmistaken about talks not continuing,
OL,20,Fas he says that conversations with the
OL,21,Freserve bidder are underway.
