OL,3,CProtest planned over 'iconic' Lido
OL,4,Cafter owner negotiations break down
OL,6,FHe adds: "There's clearly been some
OL,7,Fkind of confusion here - the process
OL,8,Fhas been followed to the letter.
OL,10,F"There have been two bids, one (Love
OL,11,FOur Lido) has pulled out, so the
OL,12,FGovernment is now talking to the
OL,13,Fsecond bidder.
OL,15,F"The reserve bidder is seeing what
OL,16,Fthey can bring to the table. They're a
OL,17,Fgroup who want to bring a community
OL,18,Foffer to the pool and make sure that
OL,19,Ffacilities for swimmers are right at
OL,20,Fthe top of the agenda."
